---
title: BBQ Pork Chops with Creamy Kale Slaw and Green Beans
description: Tender, savoury, smoky, creamy and crunchy. These are the elements you'll find in this low-carb feast! Wholesome green beans replace the starch for a lighter, yet surprisingly filling, twist on BBQ pork chops.

